When {c_important}Bone Spirit{/c} explodes inside a {c_important}Bone Prison{/c}, it explodes an additional time, dealing {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|1%|]{/c} of normal damage. 

{c_important}Bone Spirit{/c} now prioritizes enemies inside a {c_important}Bone Prison{/c}.
{c_important}Bone Spirit{/c} seeks enemies in {c_important}Bone Prison{/c}. When {c_important}Bone Spirit{/c} explodes inside {c_important}Bone Prison{/c}, it explodes an additional time.
